{"text_id":229617,"tokens":["We"," investigate"," the"," role"," of"," geodes","ics"," in"," facilitating"," the"," creation"," and"," propagation"," of"," order"," along"," Is","ing"," spin"," chains","."," Motiv","ated"," by"," the"," need"," to"," understand"," and"," control"," quantum"," many","-","body"," systems",","," we"," employ"," a"," geometric"," approach"," to"," identify"," optimal"," paths"," for"," information"," transmission"," and"," manipulation","."," Our"," methodology"," involves"," mapping"," the"," spin"," chain"," onto"," a"," geometric"," manifold",","," where"," geodes","ics"," represent"," the"," shortest"," paths"," for"," quantum"," information"," propagation","."," We"," develop"," a"," novel"," algorithm"," to"," compute"," these"," geodes","ics"," and"," demonstrate"," their"," efficacy"," in"," generating"," long","-","range"," order"," in"," Is","ing"," chains","."," Our"," results"," show"," that"," geodesic","-","based"," protocols"," outperform"," traditional"," methods",","," achieving"," faster"," and"," more"," efficient"," creation"," of"," order"," even"," in"," the"," presence"," of"," strong"," disorder"," and"," thermal"," fluctuations","."," Furthermore",","," we"," observe"," a"," significant"," reduction"," in"," the"," required"," energies"," and"," resources",","," making"," our"," approach"," promising"," for"," practical"," applications"," in"," quantum"," computing"," and"," quantum"," communication","."," Overall",","," our"," work"," establishes"," geodes","ics"," as"," a"," powerful"," tool"," for"," understanding"," and"," harness","ing"," the"," behavior"," of"," quantum"," many","-","body"," systems",","," opening"," new"," avenues"," for"," research"," in"," quantum"," information"," science","."],"sub_source":"arxiv","model":"llama3-70b","label":1}